{"tid":1838634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"28號等政府表態再決定罷工， 當日醫護界再罷唔到工","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T06:14:15.000Z","uid":189328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8427411be7340b1044a41fe4ad35da46e0e53d68","tid":1838634,"uid":189328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"政府用屎忽諗野，半年已經領教過<br />\n如果你係政府你會點解決今次單野呢？<br />\n常用方法就係唔理人， 然後返屌 醫護界轉頭， 咁唔係的話用拖字訣叫醫護界押後 罷工時間<br />\n<br />\n但政府一向冇人性又唔想同你傾有咩方法最有效阻止到你罷工，28號前 計準最多醫生護士既時間， 對外宣布封鎖醫院 黑警係可以有能力封鎖一個地方， 逼你一係做野一係就做病人， 不過政府一向知 香港人唔會見死不救所以你係裏面 一定係做野多過做病人<br />\n<br />\n所以提早罷工好過啦"},{"pid":"41a5afd8184fb33126f42716c236f96652061b23","tid":1838634,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c2cf399081c76fd9af5f199e0aad575e765060e3","tid":1838634,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"罷工罷工<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n支持醫護罷工救港</span></span>"},{"pid":"65e42a140fa15f4d31fe95b1ce198a8239cec8bd","tid":1838634,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:14:15.000Z","msg":"緊急法：醫護唔做野就即時坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}